description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Kefalonia, Greece
-Tübingen, Germany
-Kos, Greece
-Amsterdam, Netherlands
-Córdoba, Spain
-Puerto de Mogan, Spain
-Bodrum, Turkey
-Kyoto, Japan
-Spello, Italy
-Madeira, Portuguese
name: Floral Fantasies: Cities of Flowers
